@CodingOX Thank you for your timely feedback.
BTW, we encouraged  users to send PR to fix and contribute.
Many core developers (including me) because of their personal interests and use their spare time to maintain Skywalking.

@wankai123 In the previous testing, we can see the number of datasets could cause a huge payload to the backend. We are adding more metrics analysis, so we should set up perf testing for it later.
Could you add an issue to track that we should run load testing for metrics analysis service when we face 1k to 10k pods(envoys) in a single cluster?
@kezhenxu94 Your script should be able to set up this env when we do this, right?
